{"tid":1298953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【移交逃犯】林鄭：若今日說「撤回」，３個月後亦可重提","createTime":"2019-07-09T03:11:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T04:16:09.000Z","uid":36563,"like":16,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8e28b463d11d9405710dcb4ac0a42a7279727e15","tid":1298953,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:11:34.000Z","msg":"2019-07-09 10:36<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《經濟通通訊社９日專訊》行政長官林鄭月娥自７月２日凌晨後，事隔７天後終公開露面，在行政會議前見記者。她以「壽終正寢」來形容今次修例工作，但仍未正面回應是否等同完全撤回修例。<br />\n她在回應記者的追問時，指自己在早前已表示修例工作已經暫緩下來，政府亦沒有時間表，條例到明年７月就會自動失效。她直言今日的說法與之前說的並無分別，社會亦不需擔心政府會再有甚麼手段，更指就算今日說了「撤回」，政府大可以在３個月後再次重提。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=latest&amp;newsid=ETN290709690\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fwww%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fcategorized_news_detail.php%3Fcategory%3Dlatest%26newsid%3DETN290709690&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0duL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=1bc5e8f3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=latest&amp;newsid=ETN290709690</a>"},{"pid":"9844bf1dc99eb71d33430105282026086d9e93b5","tid":1298953,"uid":149630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:11:42.000Z","msg":"五大訴求唔係前設 係底綫 （同場加影七大訴求）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1298781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1298781</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"482c412b559aae4c1e221d4b9cbae785062f4d8d","tid":1298953,"uid":217275,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JPNVAkE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJPNVAkE.gif&h=2102e36c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁你講唔講呀？"},{"pid":"26a4edaa8af55f8f9c77b13bc7f34dd7bdc11977","tid":1298953,"uid":36563,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:15:31.000Z","msg":"屌你老母  <br />\n而家講撚到明  可以彈出彈入，你吹得我漲啊？<img src=\"/ass